<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mes trajets - AlloParents</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    animation: {
                        'fade-in': 'fadeIn 0.6s ease-out',
                        'slide-up': 'slideUp 0.6s ease-out',
                        'slide-in-left': 'slideInLeft 0.8s ease-out',
                        'slide-in-right': 'slideInRight 0.8s ease-out',
                        'scale-in': 'scaleIn 0.4s ease-out',
                    },
                    keyframes: {
                        fadeIn: {
                            '0%': { opacity: '0', transform: 'scale(0.95)' },
                            '100%': { opacity: '1', transform: 'scale(1)' }
                        },
                        slideUp: {
                            '0%': { transform: 'translateY(30px)', opacity: '0' },
                            '100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)', opacity: '1' }
                        },
                        slideInLeft: {
                            '0%': { transform: 'translateX(-30px)', opacity: '0' },
                            '100%': { transform: 'translateX(0)', opacity: '1' }
                        },
                        slideInRight: {
                            '0%': { transform: 'translateX(30px)', opacity: '0' },
                            '100%': { transform: 'translateX(0)', opacity: '1' }
                        },
                        scaleIn: {
                            '0%': { transform: 'scale(0.9)', opacity: '0' },
                            '100%': { transform: 'scale(1)', opacity: '1' }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        .gradient-bg {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,
                #ffffff 0%,
                #f8fafc 25%,
                #f1f5f9 50%,
                #e2e8f0 75%,
                #cbd5e1 100%
            );
        }
        
        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08), 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
        }
        
        .glass-input {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3b82f6, #2563eb, #1d4ed8);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8, #1e40af);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .btn-danger {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #dc2626, #b91c1c, #991b1b);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-danger:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #b91c1c, #991b1b, #7f1d1d);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .floating-orbs::before,
        .floating-orbs::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        
        .floating-orbs::before {
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            top: -200px;
            right: -200px;
            animation: float 15s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        .floating-orbs::after {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            bottom: -150px;
            left: -150px;
            animation: float 10s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg) translate(-20px) rotate(0deg); }
            50% { transform: rotate(180deg) translate(-20px) rotate(-180deg); }
        }

        .text-shadow {
            text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .trajet-card {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .trajet-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="gradient-bg min-h-screen">
    <!-- Background Effects -->
    <div class="floating-orbs fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none"></div>
    
    {% include 'partials/_top_navigation.html.twig' with {'pageTitle': 'Mes trajets'} %}

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="pt-24 px-4 pb-24">
        
        <!-- Flash Messages -->
        {% for message in app.flashes('success') %}
            <div class="mb-4 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm animate-scale-in">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <p class="text-emerald-700 text-sm">{{ message }}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}

        {% for message in app.flashes('error') %}
            <div class="mb-4 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm animate-scale-in">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">{{ message }}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}

        {% if error %}
            <div class="mb-4 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm animate-scale-in">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">{{ error }}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if trajets is empty %}
            <div class="glass-card rounded-3xl p-8 text-center animate-fade-in">
                <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-blue-600 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"/>
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Aucun trajet créé</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Vous n'avez pas encore créé de trajets.</p>
                <a href="{{ path('trajet_ajouter') }}" class="btn-primary text-white font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 inline-flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"/>
                    </svg>
                    Créer votre premier trajet
                </a>
            </div>
        {% else %}
            <div class="space-y-6">
                {% for trajet in trajets %}
                    <div class="glass-card rounded-3xl p-6 trajet-card animate-slide-in-left" style="animation-delay: {{ loop.index0 * 0.1 }}s">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                            <!-- Informations du trajet -->
                            <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
                                <!-- En-tête du trajet -->
                                <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
                                    <div>
                                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2 flex items-center">
                                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
                                            </svg>
                                            Trajet #{{ trajet.id }}
                                        </h3>
                                        <div class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
                                            <p class="font-medium">{{ trajet.pointDepart }}</p>
                                            <div class="flex items-center my-1">
                                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"/>
                                                </svg>
                                                <span class="text-sm">vers</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <p class="font-medium text-gray-700">{% if trajet.ecole is defined and trajet.ecole.nom is defined %}{{ trajet.ecole.nom }} - {{ trajet.ecole.ville }}{% else %}École de destination{% endif %}</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <!-- Statut -->
                                    <div class="text-right">
                                        {% if trajet.statut == 'disponible' %}
                                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-green-500/20 text-green-300 border border-green-500/30">
                                                Disponible
                                            </span>
                                        {% elseif trajet.statut == 'complet' %}
                                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-yellow-500/20 text-yellow-300 border border-yellow-500/30">
                                                Complet
                                            </span>
                                        {% elseif trajet.statut == 'en_cours' %}
                                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 border border-blue-500/30">
                                                En cours
                                            </span>
                                        {% elseif trajet.statut == 'termine' %}
                                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-gray-500/20 text-gray-300 border border-gray-500/30">
                                                Terminé
                                            </span>
                                        {% else %}
                                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-gray-500/20 text-gray-300 border border-gray-500/30">
                                                {{ trajet.statut }}
                                            </span>
                                        {% endif %}
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <!-- Détails du trajet -->
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                                    <div class="glass-input rounded-2xl p-4">
                                        <div class="flex items-center text-blue-600 mb-2">
                                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                                            </svg>
                                            <span class="font-medium text-sm">Départ</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium">{{ trajet.dateDepart }} à {{ trajet.heureDepart }}</p>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="glass-input rounded-2xl p-4">
                                        <div class="flex items-center text-blue-600 mb-2">
                                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                                            </svg>
                                            <span class="font-medium text-sm">Arrivée</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium">{{ trajet.dateArrivee }} à {{ trajet.heureArrivee }}</p>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="glass-input rounded-2xl p-4">
                                        <div class="flex items-center text-blue-600 mb-2">
                                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
                                            </svg>
                                            <span class="font-medium text-sm">Places</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium">
                                            {% set placesDisponibles = trajet.nombrePlaces - (trajet.enfantsIds|length) %}
                                            {{ placesDisponibles }} disponible{{ placesDisponibles > 1 ? 's' : '' }}
                                        </p>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="glass-input rounded-2xl p-4">
                                        <div class="flex items-center text-blue-600 mb-2">
                                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"/>
                                            </svg>
                                            <span class="font-medium text-sm">Coût</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium">{{ trajet.pointsCout ?? 5 }} points</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Description du trajet -->
                                {% if trajet.description %}
                                    <div class="glass-input rounded-2xl p-4">
                                        <div class="flex items-center text-blue-600 mb-3">
                                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
                                            </svg>
                                            <span class="font-medium text-sm">Description</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                                            <p>{{ trajet.description }}</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                {% endif %}

                                <!-- Enfants inscrits -->
                                {% if trajet.enfantsDetails is defined and trajet.enfantsDetails is not empty %}
                                    <div class="glass-input rounded-2xl p-4">
                                        <div class="flex items-center text-blue-600 mb-3">
                                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
                                            </svg>
                                            <span class="font-medium text-sm">Enfants inscrits ({{ trajet.enfantsDetails|length }})</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="space-y-3">
                                            {% for enfant in trajet.enfantsDetails %}
                                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-white/5 rounded-xl">
                                                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                                                        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                                                            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xs">{{ enfant.prenom|slice(0, 1) }}</span>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div>
                                                            <div class="text-gray-800 font-medium text-sm">{{ enfant.prenom }} {{ enfant.nom }}</div>
                                                            {% if enfant.parent is defined and enfant.parent %}
                                                                <div class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Parent: {{ enfant.parent.prenom }} {{ enfant.parent.nom }}</div>
                                                            {% endif %}
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    
                                                    <!-- Bouton de message (seulement si ce n'est pas l'enfant du conducteur) -->
                                                    {% if enfant.userId != app.user.id %}
                                                        <a href="{{ path('chat_conversation', {'trajetId': trajet.id, 'destinataireId': enfant.userId}) }}" 
                                                           class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-blue-500/30 transition-colors" 
                                                           title="Contacter le parent">
                                                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
                                                            </svg>
                                                        </a>
                                                    {% else %}
                                                        <div class="text-gray-600 text-xs">Votre enfant</div>
                                                    {% endif %}
                                                </div>
                                            {% endfor %}
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                {% endif %}
                            </div>
                            
                            <!-- Section actions -->
                            <div class="lg:border-l lg:border-white/10 lg:pl-6">
                                <div class="glass-input rounded-2xl p-4 h-full">
                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 flex items-center">
                                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4"/>
                                        </svg>
                                        Actions
                                    </h4>
                                    
                                    <div class="space-y-3">
                                        <!-- Supprimer le trajet -->
                                        <form method="post" action="{{ path('trajet_supprimer', {'id': trajet.id}) }}" class="w-full" onsubmit="return confirm('Êtes-vous sûr de vouloir supprimer ce trajet ? Cette action est irréversible.{% if trajet.enfantsIds is defined and trajet.enfantsIds is not empty %} Les utilisateurs ayant réservé seront automatiquement remboursés.{% endif %}')">
                                            <button type="submit" class="w-full btn-danger text-white font-medium py-3 px-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center">
                                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16"/>
                                                </svg>
                                                Supprimer
                                            </button>
                                        </form>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        {% endif %}
        
        <!-- Action principale -->
        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <a href="{{ path('trajet_ajouter') }}" class="btn-primary text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 inline-flex items-center transform hover:scale-105 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/20 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"/>
                </svg>
                Créer un nouveau trajet
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>

    {% include 'partials/_bottom_navigation.html.twig' %}
</body>
</html>